\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 Three or four I'm not just certain.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid471261 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 That will do fine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 Three or four years.
