But I can remember. I can remember all the blue rosettes and that sort of thing. And seeing Lord Lever in a wagonnette going round the district.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid471261 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 Now he was a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11865824\charrsid4722724 Liberal}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
