\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 Yes he was a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11865824\charrsid4722724 Liberal}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid471261 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 So they voted for a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11865824\charrsid4722724 Liberal}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
