No. You see being Scottish and being from the highlands she didn't understand the people round about her. You know she was right out of their latitude altogether.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid471261 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 So this was something she didn't do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid471261 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 
Now this perhaps wouldn't apply to you, but I'll ask you just the same. When did your father get home from work in the evenings? Now you explain why that doesn't apply.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid471261 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 He wasn't home of course, he was away at sea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 Yes. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid471261 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 Well now, when he came home, how many evenings would he spend at home? How many weeks was he home for instance when he came home? On leave.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 He was coasting you see and they came into port, say into Liverpool, and he
'd come home and perhaps the ship wouldn't be sailing for two days. Well he'd be home two evenings, and as I told you he would take us two girls out. My mother didn't bother going out very much at all. He'd buy us some fruit and things like that and alway
s took something home for my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid471261 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 Did he go out in the evenings at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 Not by himself, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid471261 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 Did he go out with your mother in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid471261 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 So he never went out in the evenings when he was home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 No. If we went out it was altogether.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid471261 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 Well he didn't go out and attend any clubs or pubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid471261 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 Never went out for a drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid471261 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 Now did he take part in any sport when he was home? Did he attend the races or did he bet at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid471261 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 He didn't go to the races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 No. There was nothing like that in our day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid471261 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 Right. Now did your father or mother belong to any savings clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid471261 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 Not at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid471261 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 I'll give you a few examples. Any boot or sick or funeral clubs, just to 
give you an idea about the kind of clubs we wanted to know about. No?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 No.
