he second school you mentioned you went to, the higher grade school, now I didn't ask you were there any children who were left out of things at that school? Can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 No. I think we were all treated the same. Absolutely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid471261 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 Now this was ab
