\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 Oh I suppose if we were going away anywhere I would buy something new for her, but I wouldn't make any statement as to when it was.

