 finish off this section. When I was talking about when you were sitting down for a meal, when the children, or Molly, were very small, what was the method of feeding and seating children too young to feed themselves. Now you remember you mentioned to me 
when you were young yourself you described how your younger sisters were fed, what about Molly when she was too young to feed herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 Oh I fed her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid471261 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 At the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 At the table in the high chair.
