\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid471261 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 You mentioned before that your mother brought you up properly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10778156 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10254032\charrsid4722724 Yes.
